---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-Hans">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>ACG Radar</title>
    <meta name="description" content="一个每小时自动更新的 ACG 资讯聚合小站（中日双语 UI）。" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 py-10">
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h1 class="m-0 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-950">ACG Radar</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">请选择语言 / 言語を選択してください</p>
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="./zh/" class="glass rounded-xl px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-950 clickable">中文</a>
          <a href="./ja/" class="glass rounded-xl px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-950 clickable">日本語</a>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          说明：本站聚合标题/摘要并跳转原文，不转载全文；数据由 GitHub Actions 每小时更新。
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
